<%= content_for :title, "HIPAA Compliance - MedGemma Health" %>
<%= content_for :meta_description, "Learn about MedGemma Health's HIPAA compliance measures and how we protect your healthcare data according to strict regulatory standards." %>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="pt-32 pb-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-green-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12" data-controller="fade-in">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-green-100 rounded-full mb-6">
        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-green-600 mr-2"></i>
        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-green-800">Security</span>
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        HIPAA 
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-teal-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Compliance
        </span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        How we protect your healthcare data according to the Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Compliance Content -->
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-green max-w-none" data-controller="fade-in">
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Commitment to HIPAA Compliance</h2>
        <p>
          At MedGemma Health, we understand the importance of protecting your medical information. We are committed to complying with the Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA) and have implemented comprehensive policies, procedures, and technologies to safeguard your Protected Health Information (PHI).
        </p>
        <p>
          As a healthcare technology company, we serve as both a Business Associate to healthcare providers and a Covered Entity when providing direct healthcare services. This dual role requires us to maintain the highest standards of data security and privacy protection.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">HIPAA Compliance Measures</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Administrative Safeguards</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Designated Privacy and Security Officers responsible for developing and implementing privacy policies</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Regular risk assessments and security evaluations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Comprehensive workforce training on HIPAA compliance</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Documented policies and procedures for handling PHI</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Business Associate Agreements with all relevant partners and vendors</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Technical Safeguards</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-blue-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>End-to-end encryption for all data in transit and at rest</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-blue-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Multi-factor authentication for all user accounts</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-blue-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Automatic session timeouts to prevent unauthorized access</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-blue-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Audit controls to track access to electronic PHI</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-blue-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Secure data backup and disaster recovery systems</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-blue-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Regular penetration testing and vulnerability assessments</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Physical Safeguards</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-purple-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Secure data centers with controlled access</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-purple-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Physical access controls including keycards and biometric authentication</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-purple-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Facility security monitoring and visitor management</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-purple-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
              <span>Device and media controls, including secure disposal procedures</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Certifications and Compliance Verification</h2>
        <p>
          MedGemma Health undergoes regular third-party audits and assessments to verify our HIPAA compliance:
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-clipboard-check text-green-600 text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">HIPAA Security Risk Assessment</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Annual comprehensive assessment conducted by independent auditors to identify and address security risks.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-blue-600 text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">SOC 2 Type II</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Service Organization Control report verifying our security, availability, and confidentiality controls.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-lock text-purple-600 text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">HITRUST CSF Certification</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Health Information Trust Alliance Common Security Framework certification demonstrating compliance with multiple regulatory frameworks.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-file-contract text-red-600 text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Business Associate Agreements</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Formal contracts with all third-party vendors who may handle PHI, ensuring compliance throughout our supply chain.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Patient Rights Under HIPAA</h2>
        <p>
          As a patient using MedGemma Health services, you have specific rights regarding your health information:
        </p>
        
        <ul class="space-y-4 mt-6">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
              <i class="fas fa-eye text-green-600"></i>
            </span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Right to Access</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">You have the right to access, review, and receive copies of your health records.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
              <i class="fas fa-edit text-green-600"></i>
            </span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Right to Amend</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">You can request corrections to your health information if you believe it is incorrect or incomplete.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
              <i class="fas fa-list-alt text-green-600"></i>
            </span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Right to an Accounting of Disclosures</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">You can request a record of when and why your health information was shared.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
              <i class="fas fa-hand-paper text-green-600"></i>
            </span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Right to Request Restrictions</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">You can ask us to limit how we use and share your health information.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
              <i class="fas fa-envelope text-green-600"></i>
            </span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Right to Confidential Communications</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">You can request that we contact you in specific ways (e.g., home or office phone) or at alternative locations.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        
        <p class="mt-6">
          To exercise any of these rights, please contact our Privacy Officer using the information provided at the bottom of this page.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Breach Notification Policy</h2>
        <p>
          Despite our best efforts to secure your information, in the unlikely event of a breach of unsecured PHI, we will:
        </p>
        
        <ul class="space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
            <span>Notify affected individuals within 60 days of discovery</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
            <span>Provide details about the breach, including what information was involved and steps to protect yourself</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
            <span>Notify the Department of Health and Human Services as required by law</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2"></i>
            <span>Notify prominent media outlets if the breach affects more than 500 individuals in a state or jurisdiction</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Contact Our Privacy Officer</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about our HIPAA compliance or wish to exercise your rights regarding your health information, please contact:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-4">
          <p class="mb-2"><strong>Privacy Officer:</strong> Jane Smith, CIPP/US</p>
          <p class="mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> privacy@medgemmahealth.com</p>
          <p class="mb-2"><strong>Phone:</strong> (800) 555-0123</p>
          <p>
            <strong>Postal Address:</strong><br>
            MedGemma Health<br>
            Attn: Privacy Officer<br>
            123 Health Avenue<br>
            San Francisco, CA 94107
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center" data-controller="fade-in">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Data Security Matters to Us</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
        Learn more about how we protect your privacy and the security measures we have in place.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/privacy" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-green-600 text-white font-medium rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors">
          <i class="fas fa-lock mr-2"></i>
          Privacy Policy
        </a>
        <a href="/security" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 font-medium rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
          <i class="fas fa-shield-alt mr-2"></i>
          Security Measures
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
